text: The Demo Album 1 is an album of demo recordings by singer/songwriter Stephen Bishop. The audio quality of the tracks vary significantly and span twenty years, from 1981 to 2001.http://www.discogs.com/Stephen-Bishop-Demo- Album-1/release/6074342 ==Track listing== All songs written by Stephen Bishop, except where noted. ==References== Category:2003 albums Category:Demo albums Category:Stephen Bishop (singer) albums
